summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2013 RAM 1500. WHILE DRIVING 25 MPH, THE PASSENGER SIDE CURTAIN AND SIDE AIR BAGS DEPLOYED, AS WELL AS THE SEAT BELT PRETENSIONER, WITHOUT WARNING OR AN IMPACT OCCURRING. THE VEHICLE WAS TAKEN TO NATIONAL DODGE CHRYSLER JEEP RAM (2223 N MARINE BLVD, JACKSONVILLE, NC 28546, (844) 872-2972) WHERE THE CONTACT WAS INFORMED THAT THERE WERE NO RECALLS ON THE VEHICLE. THE MANUFACTURER WAS MADE AWARE OF THE FAILURE AND INFORMED THE CONTACT THAT A TECHNICIAN WOULD BE SENT OUT IN TWO DAYS TO INSPECT THE VEHICLE. A COMPLAINT WAS FILED WITH THE MANUFACTURER. THE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 69,195.
